search_results.snippet: Feb 12, 2015 ... Calamity Jane was born Martha Jane Cannary, circa May 1, 1852, in Princeton, Missouri. By age 12, her parents had died and she had to make a living by any means necessary. She traveled to South Dakota and met Wild Bill Hickok in Deadwood where her legend as a hard drinking woman was born.
search_results.title: Calamity Jane - Folk Hero - Biography.com

question: She was born Martha Jane Canary in Missouri; the original "calamity" in her life may have been her parents' death
